## 🚀 Quick Start

### 1단계: 복잡한 열거형 정의

```rust
enum Message {
    Quit,
    Move { x: i32, y: i32 },
    Write(String),
    ChangeStatus(Status),
}

enum Status {
    Online,
    Offline,
}
```

### 2단계: 패턴 매칭

```rust
match message {
    Message::Quit => println!("quit"),
    Message::Move { x, y } => println!("move to ({}, {})", x, y),
    Message::Write(text) => println!("write: {}", text),
    Message::ChangeStatus(Status::Online) => println!("online"),
    _ => println!("other"),
}
```

### 3단계: Guard 패턴

```rust
match value {
    n @ 1..=10 => println!("small: {}", n),
    n @ 11..=100 => println!("medium: {}", n),
    n => println!("large: {}", n),
}
```

### 4단계: 중첩 구조분해

```rust
match event {
    Event::Command(Command::Execute { script, args }) if args.len() > 0 => {
        println!("execute: {}", script);
    }
    _ => {}
}
```

